message: "If you use OMNIAMIND or OMNIAMIND Orchestration Auditor, please cite this archived release."
title: "OMNIAMIND: Cognition-Orchestration Boundary Auditing for Measurement, Gates, Halt Signals, and External Decision Ownership"
version: "0.1.1"
date-released: "2026-05-25"
authors:
